platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: Ce qui a fait la Terre
Interact with the power of nature

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Play with interactive models to understand our planet.
La gologie naura plus de secret pour vous.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Part digital toy and part planetary handbook, The Earth gives kids insight into the workings of our world in a way thats delightfully intuitive and fun. From rockslides to earthquakes to erupting volcanoes, these artful interactive dioramas respond to tapping and swiping with results that are both whimsical and educational. An accompanying guide for parents and teachers delves into the technical science behind all these phenomena, but kids can explore, experiment, and absorb earthly knowledge at their own pace.
